com.klarna.rest.api.settlements

Class ReportsApi

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.klarna.rest.api.BaseApi
      • com.klarna.rest.api.settlements.ReportsApi

  • public class ReportsApi
extends BaseApi
    Settlements API: Reports resource. This API gives you access to your payouts and transactions. Resources are split into two broad types:
    • Collections, including pagination information: collections are queryable, typically by the attributes of the sub-resource as well as pagination
    • Entity resources containing a single entity
